      <section class="purpose">
        <h2>Purpose of Website</h2>
        <p>
          The purpose of this website is to inspire creativity and imagination
          by introducing both old and new users to Lego bricks. Through this
          site, we aim to provide a space where Lego enthusiasts can explore
          some building ideas and learn about the history of Lego. By sharing
          fun facts, starter builds, and community highlights, we hope to foster
          a sense of connection and motivation for users to build, create, and
          have fun with LEGO in new and exciting ways.
        </p>
